name: Don't Blink Media
overview: Don’t Blink Media, Inc. operates as an online advertising agency. The company offers online media buying and planning, campaign optimization, creative development, search engine optimization, and search engine marketing services. It also provides creative services, such as custom landing page development, banner packages, home page redesign, interactive flash development, identity design, testing, and optimization services. The company was founded in 2005 and is based in Seattle, Washington. As of December 11, 2007, Don’t Blink Media, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Dragon Media Online, Inc.
